# Hungry Hub

Hungry Hub is a food delivery mobile application that allows users to browse restaurants, order food, and track deliveries in real time.

## Features
- Browse restaurants and food items
- Rating-based food recommendations
- Coupon and discount system
- Real-time delivery tracking using maps
- Order placement and status updates

## Tech Stack
- Android (Kotlin/Java)
- Google Maps API
- Firebase (if used)

